name: The Gap
desc: Move one stone to complete the road.
tip: Click a stone to select it, then click a target tile to move it. A continuous chain of occupied tiles from WEST to EAST completes the level.
radius: 1
side_a: Q_NEG
side_b: Q_POS
move_limit: 1
stack: -1,0:1:1
stack: 0,-1:1:1
stack: 1,0:1:1

name: Winding Road
desc: Build a road that bends.
tip: A road is any continuous chain of occupied tiles between the highlighted sides. It does not need to be straight. Black cells block stones.
radius: 2
side_a: Q_NEG
side_b: Q_POS
move_limit: 2
blocked: -1,0
blocked: 1,0
stack: -2,0:1:1
stack: 0,-2:1:1
stack: 0,-1:1:1
stack: 0,0:1:1
stack: 0,1:1:1
stack: 0,2:1:1
stack: 2,0:1:1

name: A First Gate
desc: Merge stones to activate the gate.
tip: A value gate is active only when the top stone on that cell matches the required value exactly. Equal values merge when they touch.
radius: 1
side_a: Q_NEG
side_b: Q_POS
move_limit: 2
blocked: -1,1
blocked: 1,-1
required: 0,0:2
stack: -1,0:1:1
stack: 0,-1:1:1
stack: 0,1:1:1
stack: 1,0:1:1

name: First Height Gate
desc: Stack stones to raise the bridge.
tip: A height gate is active only when enough stones are stacked on that cell. Different values can stack without merging.
radius: 1
side_a: Q_NEG
side_b: Q_POS
move_limit: 2
blocked: -1,1
blocked: 1,-1
required_height: 0,0:2
stack: -1,0:1:1
stack: 0,-1:1:1
stack: 0,1:1:2
stack: 1,0:1:1

name: Spanning the Gap
desc: Spread a tower into a road.
tip: Drag from a stack to spread it. Spreading drops one stone on each tile along the chosen direction.
radius: 2
side_a: Q_NEG
side_b: Q_POS
move_limit: 1
stack: -2,0:1:1
stack: -1,0:1:1
stack: 0,-2:3:1,2,4
stack: 1,0:1:1
stack: 2,0:1:1
blocked: 0,1

name: Taking a Step Back
desc: Reposition before spreading.
tip: A full stack can also move one tile as a tower. The stack keeps its order when it moves.
radius: 3
side_a: Q_NEG
side_b: Q_POS
move_limit: 2
blocked: -1,1
blocked: 1,-2
stack: -3,2:1:1
stack: -2,1:1:1
stack: -1,0:1:1
stack: 1,-3:3:1,2,4
stack: 1,-1:1:1
stack: 2,-2:1:1
stack: 3,-3:1:1

name: Bridge Building
desc: Build a taller stack before crossing.
tip: Moving a tower onto another tower stacks them together. Taller stacks can spread across more tiles.
radius: 2
side_a: Q_NEG
side_b: Q_POS
move_limit: 3
blocked: 0,1
blocked: 1,-1
stack: -2,0:1:1
stack: -1,-1:2:1,4
stack: 0,-1:2:2,8
stack: 2,0:1:1

name: The Split
desc: Keep part of the tower behind.
tip: After a spread, stones that were not moved remain on the starting tile.
radius: 2
side_a: Q_NEG
side_b: Q_POS
move_limit: 3
stack: -2,0:1:1
stack: 0,0:4:1,2,4,8
stack: 2,0:1:1
blocked: -1,1
blocked: 1,-1

name: Two Tolls
desc: Open a road through value and height gates.
tip: A value gate checks the top stone. A height gate checks stack height. Both must be active for the road to count.
radius: 3
side_a: Q_NEG
side_b: Q_POS
move_limit: 3
blocked: -1,1
blocked: 0,1
blocked: 1,-2
blocked: 1,0
required: 0,0:4
