name: Diagonal Run
desc: Connect along another axis.
tip: Hex tiles have six directions. A valid road can follow any of them.
radius: 2
side_a: R_NEG
side_b: R_POS
move_limit: 3
stack: 0,-2:1:1
stack: 0,-1:1:1
stack: -1,0:3:1,2,4
stack: 1,0:1:1
stack: 0,2:1:1
blocked: 0,0

name: Around the Block
desc: Bend around the obstacle.
tip: Blocked tiles cannot be crossed or occupied. A valid road may need to leave the obvious line.
